item.title: About
item.description: Dulguun Gantumur An IR student at George Mason University interested in topics ranging from linguistics, philosophy, and Central Asia. Languages I currently speak English, Mongolian, Mandarin Chinese fluently, and actively learning Azerbaijani with plans of Russian in the future.
